data.description: Welcome home to 6552 Sabinal. This gorgeous home located in the Luckey Ranch community is ready for its new owners. Featuring updated laminate flooring, granite counters in the kitchen, fresh paint throughout, and a faux fireplace feature in the living room. The backyard is set up and ready for entertaining on the deck and includes an above ground pool for friends and family to enjoy. Community amenites offer plenty of options for the whole family. Now open is the brand-new, $2 million sports park. This includes two playgrounds, a splash pad, a basketball court, a soccer field, a baseball field, a 7-acre fishing lake with a pier.
